{"tid":1058272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"World Wide Web 誕生 30 周年　萬維網之父：現今網絡世界嚴重功能失調","createTime":"2019-03-12T12:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T01:04:16.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dbcb9fe170f016b3ebd179b47fe69ab51c0a3324","tid":1058272,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T12:12:02.000Z","msg":"由無數網頁組成的萬維網「World Wide Web」在 1989 年面世至今，剛好 30 周年。經過多年發展，這個系統已經和現代人類生活密不可分。不過當年發明這套系統的萬維網之父，英國科學家 Tim Berners Lee 卻對現代的網絡世界感到十分不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCaSmTu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCaSmTu.png&h=350fe9f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他在昨日發出公開信，指今日的萬維網已經出現嚴重的功能失調，更直指網絡的力量已不再是一股善良的力量。在公開信中，他更點名批評以 Facebook及 Google 為首的科技公司，採用廣告分成的營利模式，與為標題黨及假新聞來源背書無異。此外，他亦指近年常見的網絡攻擊行為，是令到萬維網出現問題的第二個罪魁禍首。<br />\n<br />\n為扭轉目前網上世界中的各種問題， Berners Lee 認為企業及政府責無旁貸，當中私人企業需要採取行動，確保他們的營利方式能夠保障人權、民主及科學等重要價值。而政府亦應該要及時修改法例，適度監管互聯網，在不威脅互聯網開放的前題下，阻止網路攻擊及騷擾行為。<br />\n<br />\n最後， Berners Lee 同時指責網絡上愈來愈多極端言論，更表示沒有想過萬維網的發明會導致這個後果。不過他認為，所有人都應該為網上出現極端言論而負責，共同守護這一片網上空間。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：BBC<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/03/12/www-30/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2Fwww-30%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0Lay3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=a8bff8ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/03/12/www-30/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"8209153169e6240e635c2058f803da6fd02fdefa","tid":1058272,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T12:15:47.000Z","msg":"封信：<br />\n<a href=\"https://webfoundation.org/2019/03/web-birthday-30/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebfoundation.org%2F2019%2F03%2Fweb-birthday-30%2F&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0Lay3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=651abae0\" target=\"_blank\">https://webfoundation.org/2019/03/web-birthday-30/</a><br />\n<br />\n當年整互聯網既計劃書：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/History/1989/proposal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2FHistory%2F1989%2Fproposal.html&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0Lay3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=99a73ce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.w3.org/History/1989/proposal.html</a>"},{"pid":"77470c81c5c1dd0229d13f96290a3f9d3867a6a3","tid":1058272,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T12:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c837755b60e7dac52faa5a524ea498e2f80ff7e","tid":1058272,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T00:45:51.000Z","msg":"microsoft 係 html 加勁多私人野都扭曲唔少網頁設定"},{"pid":"5ef1128cc52e0bb06d84449adfa7c9e02bbdaf51","tid":1058272,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T00:52:36.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca9affe4713bf63684aca03de560028b7c0eaee","tid":1058272,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T01:00:00.000Z","msg":"有鹹野睇先帶動www<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b43f65cc366d4c4bccb7cb0a0c90cc07182dd8","tid":1058272,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T01:04:16.000Z","msg":"廿年前都好撚多廣告啦"}]}